(6, 76, 'Accomodation', '2015-09-18-15-18-35', '<h1 class=" cmsheading   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 14px; font-size: 24px; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal; color: #9f0606; font-stretch: normal; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="8">Discover stunning vistas, superb boutique rooms, and unrivaled service</h1>\r\n<p class=" cmsparagraph   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="9">With two neighboring buildings, offering both business and leisure travelers outstanding services and comfort, in 71 rooms and 19 suites, all custom fit with rich furnishings, and excellent in-room amenities, Myros Hotel stands in<img style="float: left; padding: 5px;" src="images/blue-hotel-1234804.jpg" alt="" width="240" height="184" /> one of the best locations in Heraklion city, right above the old harbor, with <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">unrestricted views to the Venetian fortress</span>. <br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">Book directly on our site</span> and get <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">exclusive rates</span> and <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">special customer care</span>. We guarantee the <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">best online prices</span> for direct bookings.</p>\r\n<p class=" cmsparagraph   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="9"> </p>', '