(7, 77, 'Cuisine', '2015-09-18-15-18-53', '<p class=" cmsparagraph   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="81">With its buoyant, yet luxurious atmosphere, Brillant Restaurant offers <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">unique culinary experiences</span>since 2007. Fine raw local ingredients, cooked with imagination and respect towards authentic <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">Cretan</span> <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">traditions</span>, result in delicious dishes. The selection varies every season, and themed evenings add an adventurous plus to an <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">incomparable à la carte menu</span>. The restaurant is open daily from noon till late at night, from <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">November to May</span>, when it passes the torch to Herbs’ Garden to welcome the Cretan spring.</p>\r\n<div id="brillantrestaurantcollapsible" class=" cmsrichtext   " style="box-sizing: border-box; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="72">\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify;"><img style="float: left; padding: 5px;" src="images/dining-room-103464_640.jpg" alt="" width="459" height="304" />With a vivid color scheme, and subtle tropical motifs, Brillant is ideal for romantic dinners, private events,</p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify;">and business meetings. Guests will savor <span style="box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;">nouvelle Grecque cuisine</span> for lunch or dinner: fine local meat dishes, wild green salads, hand-made pasta, fresh fish and delicious homemade desserts, paired with selected wines, or refreshing cocktails.<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />The atmosphere is enhanced with carefully picked tunes and live bands weekly. Perhaps Brillant’s best attribute, this is a place where upscale doesn’t mean expensive. Call it affordable fine dining, if you will, and come to find out why our restaurant is counted among the best in Crete.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', 1, 9, '2015-09-18 15:18:53', 553, '', '2015-09-20 22:46:54', 553, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-18 15:18:53', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":"","show_create_date":"","show_modify_date":"","show_publish_date":"","show_item_navigation":"","show_icons":"","show_print_icon":"","show_email_icon":"","show_vote":"","show_hits":"","show_noauth":"","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":"","post_format":"standard","gallery":"","audio":"","video":"","link_title":"","link_url":"","quote_text":"","quote_author":"","post_status":""}', 20, 2, '', '', 1, 37, '{"robots":"","author":"","rights":"","xreference":""}', 0, '*', ''),
