(11, 101, 'Standard room', 'standard-room', '<h2 class=" cmsheading   " style="box-sizing: border-box; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; line-height: normal; color: #9f0606; margin: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 20px; font-stretch: normal; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="14">Standard Rooms</h2>\r\n<p class=" cmsparagraph   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="15">18m<span style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; font-size: 11.25px; line-height: 0; vertical-align: baseline; top: -0.5em;">2</span>, sleeps up to 2 persons,<br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />Double bed, or Twin beds <br style="box-sizing: border-box;" /><br style="box-sizing: border-box;" />Relaxed and stylish, the Standard Rooms are beyond “standard hotel rooms.”</p>\r\n<p class=" cmsparagraph   " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f4f4f4;" data-component-id="15"><img src="images/standard_rooms/hotel-rooms6977s.jpg" alt="" width="265" height="199" />  </p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">Completely refurbished, our Standard Rooms are located on the mezzanine floor and on the ground floor of the annex building, and at the first floor of the hotel''s main building. The rooms offer views to the city or to the open space in front of the annex building. Ground floor rooms have private access to a beautiful courtyard located at the rear of the property </p>\r\n<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">Facilities, equipment and amenities in Standard Rooms:</p>\r\n<div class="row " style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-right: -15px; margin-left: -15px; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; background-color: #f4f4f4;">\r\n<div class="col-md-6 col-sm-6 bulletList" style="box-sizing: border-box; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-right: 15px; padding-left: 15px; float: left; width: 580px;">\r\n<ul style="box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px;">\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Superior quality mattresses, with exclusive duvets and bed linen</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Work desk</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Automatic high security door locks</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Electronic safe</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Individually controlled air conditioning</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Free high speed Internet access (WiFi and wired)</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Satellite plasma TV</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Μini-bar</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Direct telephone line with voicemail &amp; DDI</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Fully sound-absorbing (glazed) framed structures for thermal break</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Fire alarm system</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Elegant bathroom with shower</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Organic personal care products and modern bathroom devices</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Direct telephone line in the bathroom</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Hair dryer</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Room service</li>\r\n<li style="box-sizing: border-box; text-align: justify;">Laundry and dry cleaning services</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;">Price 60 euro/person.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="line-height: 20px; text-align: justify;"><a href="index.php/en/hotel-myros-hotel">Book Now!</a> </span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '', 1, 19, '2015-09-20 21:44:38', 553, '', '2015-09-20 23:11:03', 553, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2015-09-20 21:44:38', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"0","link_titles":"0","show_tags":"0","show_intro":"0","info_block_position":"","show_category":"0","link_category":"0","show_parent_category":"0","link_parent_category":"0","show_author":"0","link_author":"0","show_create_date":"0","show_modify_date":"0","show_publish_date":"0","show_item_navigation":"0","show_icons":"0","show_print_icon":"0","show_email_icon":"0","show_vote":"0","show_hits":"0","show_noauth":"0","urls_position":"","alternative_readmore":"","article_layout":"","show_publishing_options":"","show_article_options":"","show_urls_images_backend":"","show_urls_images_frontend":"","post_format":"standard","gallery":"","audio":"","video":"","link_title":"","link_url":"","quote_text":"","quote_author":"","post_status":""}', 21, 2, '', '', 1, 10, '{"robots":"","author":"