(152, 7, 1, '', '2015-09-20 22:46:54', 553, 4549, 'de781860cc329c29ede3498b39cb5441a357dddb', '{"id":7,"asset_id":"77","title":"Cuisine","alias":"2015-09-18-15-18-53","introtext":"<p class=\\" cmsparagraph   \\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; text-align: justify; background-color: #f4f4f4;\\" data-component-id=\\"81\\">With its buoyant, yet luxurious atmosphere, Brillant Restaurant offers\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">unique culinary experiences<\\/span>since 2007. Fine raw local ingredients, cooked with imagination and respect towards authentic\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">Cretan<\\/span>\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">traditions<\\/span>, result in delicious dishes. The selection varies every season, and themed evenings add an adventurous plus to an\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">incomparable \\u00e0 la carte menu<\\/span>. The restaurant is open daily from noon till late at night, from\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">November to May<\\/span>, when it passes the torch to Herbs\\u2019 Garden to welcome the Cretan spring.<\\/p>\\r\\n<div id=\\"brillantrestaurantcollapsible\\" class=\\" cmsrichtext   \\" style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; color: #4a4a4a; font-family: ''Century Gothic'', Verdana, Geneva, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; line-height: normal; background-color: #f4f4f4;\\" data-component-id=\\"72\\">\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify;\\"><img style=\\"float: left; padding: 5px;\\" src=\\"images\\/dining-room-103464_640.jpg\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"459\\" height=\\"304\\" \\/>With a vivid color scheme, and subtle tropical motifs, Brillant is ideal for romantic dinners, private events,<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 20px; padding-bottom: 8px; text-align: justify;\\">and business meetings. Guests will savor\\u00a0<span style=\\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: bold;\\">nouvelle Grecque cuisine<\\/span>\\u00a0for lunch or dinner: fine local meat dishes, wild green salads, hand-made pasta, fresh fish and delicious homemade desserts, paired with selected wines, or refreshing cocktails.<br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" \\/><br style=\\"box-sizing: border-box;\\" \\/>The atmosphere is enhanced with carefully picked tunes and live bands weekly. Perhaps Brillant\\u2019s best attribute, this is a place where upscale doesn\\u2019t mean expensive. Call it affordable fine dining, if you will, and come to find out why our restaurant is counted among the best in Crete.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/div>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"9","created":"2015-09-18 15:18:53","created_by":"553","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-09-20 22:46:54","modified_by":"553","checked_out":"553","checked_out_time":"2015-09-20 22:46:41","publish_up":"2015-09-18 15:18:53","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"